<section>
  <h2 class="page-header"><a href="#buttons">Buttons <code>&lbrace;&lbrace;rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</code></a></h2>
  <p>A button is used to trigger an immediate action such as form submission. Buttons should not be used for navigation.</p>
  <p>An <code>rui-button</code> block renders an HTML <code>button</code> element. The <code>button</code>'s content&thinsp;—&thinsp;text, an icon, or both&thinsp;—&thinsp;is contained within the <code>rui-button</code> block and passed through safely.</p>

  <h3>Properties</h3>
  <h4><a href="#button-styles">Styles</a></h4>
  <p>Button styles provide context through visual cues. <code>style</code> is a required attribute.</p>
  <dl class="dl-horizontal list-group">
    <span class="list-group-item">
      <dt>Style:</dt>
      <dd>[string]</dd>
    </span>
    <span class="list-group-item">
      <dt>Available values:</dt>
      <dd>'standard', 'primary', 'success', 'info', 'warning', 'danger', 'link'</dd>
    </span>
    <span class="list-group-item">
      <dd>Required attribute</dd>
    </span>
  </dl>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <strong class="text-uppercase text-muted">Example</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      {{#rui-button style="standard"}}Standard{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="primary"}}Primary{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="success"}}Success{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="info"}}Info{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="warning"}}Warning{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="danger"}}Danger{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="link"}}Link{{/rui-button}}
      {{#rui-button style="standard"}}<i class="fa fa-download" />{{/rui-button}}
    </div>
    <div class="panel-footer">
      <pre>
  <code><span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Standard Button --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"standard"</span><span class="text-info">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Standard<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Provides visual weight and identifies the primary action in a set of buttons --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"primary"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Primary<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Indicates a successful or positive action --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"success"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Success<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Contextual button for informational alert messages --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"info"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Info<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Indicates caution should be taken with this action --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"warning"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Warning<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Indicates a dangerous or potentially negative action --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"danger"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Danger<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- Deemphasize a button by making it look like a link while maintaining button behavior --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"link"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>Link<span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>

  <span class="text-muted">&lt;!-- FontAwesome icons can be used in lieu of or in addition to text --&gt;</span>
  <span class="text-primary">&lbrace;&lbrace;#rui-button</span> <span class="text-warning">style=</span><span class="text-danger">"standard"</span><span class="text-primary">&rbrace;&rbrace;&lt;i </span><span class="text-warning">class=</span><span class="text-danger">&quot;fa fa-download&quot;</span><span class="text-primary"> /&gt;&lbrace;&lbrace;/rui-button&rbrace;&rbrace;</span></code>
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>

